{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75484a899d","title":"关于在党内传达中苏两党会谈记录的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0bc555abdc","index":0,"year":1963,"month":7,"day":28,"articleId":"75484a899d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"5972e4500b","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"75484a899d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央总书记邓小平报送的由中央书记处书记康生写的请示报告上。报告说，现在，有不少单位提出要求，希望了解中苏两党会谈的情况。这种要求是完全可以理解的。我们考虑，可否将两党九次会谈的记录，在党内十七级以上干部中念一次。这对党内干部的反修教育，是有好处的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ab0d8f343f","type":"title","text":"关于在党内传达中苏两党会谈记录的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"75484a899d"},{"id":"5972e4500b","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"75484a899d"},{"id":"c15550ec84","type":"paragraph","text":"单是念不够，似应印发，十七级以上干部每若干人一本（例如三人或五人一本），以便他们讨论研究。三个月后，一律收回。请耐定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"75484a899d"},{"id":"aa9f80f009","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"75484a899d"},{"id":"4833f705aa","type":"paragraph","text":"廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"75484a899d"}],"page":{"id":"f6ae6bf7f8","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"75484a899d","start":488,"end":488}}}},"__N_SSG":true}